ge.com/23951136/gifts- under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget</id><author><name>边缘人员</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-23T16:04:42-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-23T16:04:42-05:00</updated><title> The Verge 为妈妈们准备的 2023 年节日礼物指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;照片插图，手拿着各种产品，背景是明亮的星星。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/L6N2nmWpZ-tCeYFFnr6LkNtS70I=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875697/236830_FOR_MOMS_Gift_Guide_ Artboards_CVirginia_LEDE_2040x1360.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片插图由 Amelia Holowaty Krales 和 Cath Virginia / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;一系列炫酷、平静且富有创意的礼物，以表达您对生活中特殊母亲形象的欣赏.&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23955826/holiday-gifts-mom-unique-ideas-2023-tech-gadgets</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-23T14:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-23T14:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Unicorn Overlord 旨在将战术角色扮演游戏带回到 90 年代</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;视频游戏 Unicorn Overlord 的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BeOcS3PitJ1AFP_PpBRwKWo2Gls=/300x0:1920x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72896281/UO_Clive_Discuss.0.png&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Atlus&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9Op2e4&quot;>;Vanillaware 比任何其他游戏工作室都以其风格而闻名。与此同时，开发者&lt;em>;不断&lt;/em>;在游戏类型之间切换。它最初凭借横向卷轴动作角色扮演游戏《Odin Sphere》引起轰动，最近又发布了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21493208/13-sentinels-aegis-rim- ps4-review-vanillaware&quot;>;科幻史诗《十三哨兵》&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;，部分是视觉小说，部分是回合制机甲大战怪兽战斗。将所有这些不同的想法结合在一起就是 Vanillaware 令人难以置信的 2D 艺术，以及明确的实验欲望。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;G7jQLN&quot;>;考虑到工作室如此喜欢跳来跳去，这可能并不太令人惊讶其下一个项目《Unicorn Overlord》将是一款受经典启发的大型战术角色扮演游戏。在游戏于明年 3 月发布之前（将登陆 PlayStation、Xbox 和 Switch）...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/ 23971097/unicorn-overlord-retro-战术-rpg-interview-switch-xbox-playstation&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23971097/unicorn-overlord-retro-tactical-rpg-interview-switch-xbox-playstation" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/23/23971097/unicorn-overlord-retro-tropical-rpg-interview-switch-xbox-playstation</id><author><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name></author></entry></feed>